&lt;span class="kn"&gt;lemma&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;"f -` (u ∪ v) = f -` u ∪ f -` v"&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="gr"&gt;sorry&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="k"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

